    <note>Du(3) Chun [1724] Yuanyou coalition. His ancestors were Jingzhao, Wannian xian Du(3). They later moved to Puzhou, Quancheng xian. He was the son-in-law of Chao(2) Duanyan's [14] lineage uncle, Chao(2) Zhongcan [3013]. He was the father-in-law of Chao(2) Buzhi [13], Ma(2) Xiyue [3666], the son of Ma(2) Yuanfang's [1355]'s grandson, Ma(2) Sui [3668], and of Cui(1) Gongru's [7358] probable nephew, Cui(1) Yansun [3886]. His son, Qinxue [3914], died at the age of 19 after having married Yan(4) Shi. His brother, Hong [3919], was Han(1) Lian's [7230] father-in-law. He was the father of Du(3) Kai [3918], the son-in-law of Chao(2) Buzhi's [13] lineage uncle, Chao(2) Duanben [3024]. Recommended by Wen(2) Yanbo [1953] Chao Buzhi, WJ, 62.6a-14b, 66.12b, 67.15a, 68.9a; XCB, 394.17a, 412.4a, 4a (n.), 415.11a, 418.2a. CBD, 2, 798-9.</note>
